title: Trump’s Iowa Rally Is About More Than the Midterms
description: Former President Donald J. Trump is eager to announce a new bid for the White House, and Iowa holds outsize importance. His Thursday night event will support two incumbents.
dc:creator: Michael C. Bender

media:content.media:credit: Rebecca Noble for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Former President Donald J. Trump has hosted campaign rallies in several midterm battleground states, including Arizona last month. He heads to Iowa on Thursday for a rally that is as much about a possible presidential race as about the incumbents he’ll be supporting.
